OL,6,FA retired woman who lost #10,500 after
OL,7,Fbeing scammed on Instagram whilst
OL,8,Fbuying garden furniture fears she'll
OL,9,Fnever get her savings back.
OL,11,F66-year-old Sian Brooker from Cwmbran
OL,12,Fwas scrolling through the social media
OL,13,Fchannel when she spotted what she
OL,14,Fthought was a good offer online.
OL,16,FLittle did she know at the time that
OL,17,Fthat #22 purchase would end up costing
OL,18,Fher over #10,000.
