OL,6,FSian says it was her worst nightmare
OL,7,Fwhen she realised she had fallen
OL,8,Fvictim to scammers and had lost her
OL,9,Fretirement money.
OL,11,FShe told ITV Wales the whole
OL,12,Fexperience has been "really upsetting".
OL,14,FSian said: "I was on Instagram, I saw
OL,15,Fthis sun lounger and I thought oh that
OL,16,Flooks good and it was a reasonable
OL,17,Fprice. I thought I'll order that.
