OL,6,F"I filled my details in and then at
OL,7,Fthe bottom it said Apple Pay, I don't
OL,8,Fhave that so I came off the site. I
OL,9,Fthen had a text message off the Co-Op
OL,10,Fasking have you authorised Apple Pay.
OL,12,F"I thought, oh, they must know a way
OL,13,Fof doing it, so I authorised the
OL,14,Fpayment and it stemmed from there."
OL,16,FInitially, Sian couldn't bring herself
OL,17,Fto tell her family. She said: "I was
OL,18,Fhorrified. I thought how am I going to
OL,19,Ftell Ryan? (her son) What do I say to
OL,20,Fhim? Because I hadn't told him for a
OL,21,Fcouple of days.
