OL,6,FA tearful Sian said: "It upsets me
OL,7,Fbecause it is my pension money. I lost
OL,8,Fmy husband the year before, so I was
OL,9,Fstill grieving over that. And I look
OL,10,Fand I think he'd be thinking 'you
OL,11,Fstupid woman', you know."
OL,13,FShe added how it has affected her
OL,14,Fsaying she hasn't been able to sleep.
OL,15,FShe said: "Normally I go to bed about
OL,16,Fhalf past ten and I don't have any
OL,17,Fproblem sleeping whatsoever but it was
OL,18,Fgetting later and later.
