OL,6,FShe said: "It was even getting to the
OL,7,Fstage that I was having to have a
OL,8,Fdrink to get me off to sleep and then
OL,9,FI would wake up just thinking about it
OL,10,Fand crying about it. Thinking there is
OL,11,Fnothing I can do about it."
OL,13,FSian left her job in 2023 and says she
OL,14,Fis "getting by" on her state pension
OL,15,Fand her late husband's pension. But
OL,16,Fsays the money that was taken was set
OL,17,Faside for her to buy a new car. She
OL,18,Fsays that's now "on hold" and she
OL,19,Fdoesn't think she'll ever be able to
OL,20,Fchange her car.
