OL,6,FHer son Ryan has been dealing with her
OL,7,Fcase on her behalf and he says he's
OL,8,Ffrustrated by the lack of
OL,9,Fcommunication from the Co-op bank.
OL,11,FHe said: "It's heartbreaking,
OL,12,Fabsolutely heartbreaking. For me, I
OL,13,Fcan't understand how all these
OL,14,Fseparate amounts for the same values -
OL,15,Fyou've got nine lots of #508 and 7
OL,16,Flots of #682, and they all appear to
OL,17,Fbe abroad where they've got the
OL,18,Ftransaction cost, surely that
OL,19,Fshould've flagged up somewhere.
OL,20,FThey've just got no care or compassion
OL,21,Fat all."
