OL,6,FSian hopes her story will raise
OL,7,Fawareness so other people won't go
OL,8,Fthrough what she has.
OL,10,FShe said: "You hear of people being
OL,11,Fscammed but I didn't think for one
OL,12,Fminute I would get scammed and I can't
OL,13,Fbelieve people can do that. How would
OL,14,Fthey feel if it was their mother? or
OL,15,Ftheir grandmother, being scammed? It's
OL,16,Fnot a very nice feeling."
OL,18,FA spokesperson for the Co-op bank
OL,19,Fsaid: "At The Co-operative Bank,
OL,20,Fprotecting our customers against fraud
OL,21,Fis of the utmost importance.
