OL,6,F"Fraudsters are becoming increasingly
OL,7,Fsophisticated and this particular case
OL,8,Fhighlights the importance of staying
OL,9,Fvigilant and why you should never
OL,10,Fshare key account or security
OL,11,Finformation or approve transactions
OL,12,Fyou have not made.
OL,14,F"We want to reassure our customers
OL,15,Fthat we have robust security controls
OL,16,Fin place to protect them from fraud.
OL,17,FWe do ask that customers remain
OL,18,Fvigilant when it comes to suspicious
OL,19,Factivity on their accounts and never
OL,20,Fconfirm any transactions as genuine
OL,21,Funless they are completely sure.
